  <excerpt>Congratulations on your new blog</excerpt>
  <content>&lt;h2 id="1f74" class="fm fn dc bk bj fo de fp dg fq fr fs ft fu fv fw fx" style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 默认; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.618; color: #3c4858; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-size: 37px;"&gt;Namesilo 简介&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p id="e504" class="fy fz dc bk ga b gb gc gd ge gf gg gh gi gj gk gl cu" style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.618; color: #3c4858; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;" data-selectable-paragraph=""&gt;&lt;a class="at cg gr gs gt gu" style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-color: transparent; color: #e91e63; text-decoration-line: none; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s;" href="https://www.namesilo.com/?rid=aecc848vc" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;Namesilo&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;是 ICANN 认证的国际著名域名注册商之一，&lt;span class="md_line" style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"&gt;价格便宜实惠、性价比高&lt;/span&gt;，注册和转入域名都很方便，安全保护到位，是一家非常靠谱的域名注册商。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.618; color: #3c4858; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;" data-selectable-paragraph=""&gt;&lt;strong style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"&gt;注意：&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; line-height: 1.618; font-size: 18px; color: #3c4858; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;
&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"&gt;部分网友反馈支付宝付款后域名列表为空，请发工单需要联系客服；&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"&gt;如果中文不好，或者打开网页很慢，建议到国内的阿里云、腾讯云、百度云等网站去注册。国内买域名的&lt;strong style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"&gt;缺点主要是需要实名认证(要上传身份证)、可供注册的顶级域名数量少&lt;/strong&gt;。注册域名后设置dns解析到vps的ip也一样能使用。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h3 class="fy fz dc bk ga b gb gc gd ge gf gg gh gi gj gk gl cu" style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 默认; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.618; color: #3c4858; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-size: 32px;"&gt;Namesilo有如下优点：&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h4 id="3074" class="fy fz dc bk ga b gb gc gd ge gf gg gh gi gj gk gl cu" style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 默认; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.618; color: #3c4858; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-size: 27px;"&gt;&lt;strong class="ga gv" style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"&gt;1. 价格便宜稳定，无套路&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p id="2b34" class="fy fz dc bk ga b gb gm gd gn gf go gh gp gj gq gl cu" style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.618; color: #3c4858; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;" data-selectable-paragraph=""&gt;Namesilo 域名本身价格就比较便宜，com域名 8.99刀每年(几乎市场最低价)，除了一个一美元新手优惠码(优惠码&amp;nbsp;&lt;code class="gw gx gy gz ha b prettyprinted" style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 16.2px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; background-color: #f9f2f4; border-radius: 4px;"&gt;&lt;span class="pln" style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"&gt;hijk&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;，订单金额需大于1刀)，基本没有其他大幅度促销活动，域名续费和首年购买价格一致。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p id="faf4" class="fy fz dc bk ga b gb gc gd ge gf gg gh gi gj gk gl cu" style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.618; color: #3c4858; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;" data-selectable-paragraph=""&gt;某些域名注册商就套路满满，首年极其便宜（例如1刀），先套住你再说。但续费很贵（15刀），隐私保护还要额外收费 ，续费不可以使用优惠码。如果不对比其他家，你甚至都发现不了这些套路。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.618; color: #3c4858; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;Namesilo价格表：&lt;a class="at cg gr gs gt gu" style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-color: transparent; color: #e91e63; text-decoration-line: none; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s;" href="https://www.namesilo.com/pricing.php?rid=aecc848vc" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;Domain Pricing&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 id="c1c4" class="fy fz dc bk ga b gb gm gd gn gf go gh gp gj gq gl cu" style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 默认; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.618; color: #3c4858; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-size: 27px;"&gt;&lt;strong class="ga gv" style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"&gt;2. 永久免费的隐私保护&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p id="3c48" class="fy fz dc bk ga b gb gm gd gn gf go gh gp gj gq gl cu" style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.618; color: #3c4858; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;" data-selectable-paragraph=""&gt;&lt;a style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-color: transparent; color: #e91e63; text-decoration-line: none; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s;" href="https://www.namesilo.com/?rid=aecc848vc" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;Namesilo&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;提供永久免费的域名隐私保护，防止别人通过 WHOIS 查询获取域名所有者的个人注册信息。作为对比，Godaddy 的隐私保护是 60 元/年。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 id="8521" class="fy fz dc bk ga b gb gm gd gn gf go gh gp gj gq gl cu" style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 默认; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.618; color: #3c4858; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-size: 27px;"&gt;&lt;strong class="ga gv" style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"&gt;3. 安全性高&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p id="0898" class="fy fz dc bk ga b gb gm gd gn gf go gh gp gj gq gl cu" style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.618; color: #3c4858; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;" data-selectable-paragraph=""&gt;支持账户登陆二次验证和 Domain Defender，保护账户和域名安全。登陆、解锁域名等，可以设置邮件或短信提醒。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 id="e5ef" class="fy fz dc bk ga b gb gm gd gn gf go gh gp gj gq gl cu" style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 默认; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.618; color: #3c4858; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-size: 27px;"&gt;&lt;strong class="ga gv" style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"&gt;4. 支付方便&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p id="7b3b" class="fy fz dc bk ga b gb gm gd gn gf go gh gp gj gq gl cu" style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.618; color: #3c4858; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;" data-selectable-paragraph=""&gt;支持支付宝、Paypal、信用卡等多种方式付款。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 默认; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.618; color: #3c4858; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-size: 32px;"&gt;Namesilo的缺点：&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p id="ec2f" class="fy fz dc bk ga b gb gc gd ge gf gg gh gi gj gk gl cu" style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.618; color: #3c4858; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;" data-selectable-paragraph=""&gt;1. 网站后台风格过时简陋，功能繁多，面板功能不好找；&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="fy fz dc bk ga b gb gc gd ge gf gg gh gi gj gk gl cu" style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.618; color: #3c4858; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;" data-selectable-paragraph=""&gt;2. 没有中文界面；&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.618; color: #3c4858; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;" data-selectable-paragraph=""&gt;3. 自带的DNS解析生效很慢，TTL最低3600秒(可以&lt;a style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-color: transparent; color: #e91e63; text-decoration-line: none; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s;" href="https://www.hijk.pw/use-cloudflare-unlock-blocked-ip/#change-dns"&gt;切换到免费CloudFlare&lt;/a&gt;解决)。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.618; color: #3c4858; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;" data-selectable-paragraph=""&gt;接下来让我们进入域名注册的流程吧！&lt;/p&gt;</content>
